The paper proposes a new principle for unsupervised domain adaptation and analyzes the relationship between decision boundary and features in terms of smoothness. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM).
